<br>
The people that play monks at the FOH/AL level of the game are the ones who should have been nerfed. Contrary to what some people might believe, monks are not all equipped with 1500ac and 4500hp unbuffed. Broadstroking the class into that category is stupid. <br>
<br>
My point is do some investigation on your own before you subscribe blindly to some parsing that the warrior god has blessed you all with. Use your own eyes. Ask how many monks on your server would be willing to tank Vindi/AOW any of the uber unslowable mobs and youll see exactly what kinda tanks we are. They will most likely laugh at you. Monks are not tanks and never will be. We dont have the discs or HP for it. Stepping up for a few seconds is one thing, tanking from beginning to end is a whole different ballgame. We dont play that game.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ushikariiapoccalypse.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shikarii Apoccalypse</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>All in the reflexes</BR>Guardian of the Bunker</BR>STEEL WARRIOR Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 1967<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/11/02 7:16:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1398.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.wingkong.net/Images/minijak.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Just one question</span><hr size=1> And the Capital of Nebraska is Lincoln.<br>
<br>
Thanks for playing and as your runner-up prize you've been enrolled in the Jelly of the Month Club; the gift that keeps on giving. <p><center><img src=http://publish.hometown.aol.com/crushr85/myhomepage/new_vincent.jpg><BR>
Baron Shikarii T'Zaii - <A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=172088">Warlord</A> - <A HREF="http://www.divinelegend.com">Divine Legend</A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uantiuber.showPublicProfile?language=EN>antiuber</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 87<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/11/02 8:07:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1398.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www2.satexas.com/~tawdry/ofo.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Just one question</span><hr size=1>   The nerf, as it has become known. I dont think had anything to do with warriors asking for it. I have not seen a post of that nature from anyone really. I will admit though some posts from monks on this board that I read made one heck of a case for a good nerf. <br>
  Warriors asked to be fixed no more no less. We asked for better mitigation, dps and to fix taunt. I dont think our concerns have even been addressed to be honest. I guess the reason monks think warriors are behind the nerf is cause we asked to be looked at and in doing so VI noticed that monks are over powered and not working as intended. <br>
  I am surprised VI took this course of action and do not enjoy anyones nerf, but no monk can sit there with a straight face and say &quot; Oh wait we really wernt as good as we said we were..umm we were just kidding...you guys are better tanks...really you are&quot; <p><BR>
<p>
<p align=LEFT><i>Baron</i> <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=170375 ><B>Quig McQuaid</a> </B>Warlord<BR><B><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=262944 >Emar Bloodwood</a> </B>Pathfinder<BR><B><Font color=Red>O</font>rder of the <Font color=Red>F</font>allen <Font color=Red>O</font>nes</B><BR><i>Officer and Sgt at Arms</i><BR><B>The</B> Waste of Time!</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uwubaogoldenarmz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wubao Goldenarmz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 205<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/11/02 8:54:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1398.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   wait just a second now ...</span><hr size=1> Lincoln Nebraska?<br>
<br>
What's the capital of South Dakota then?<br>
<br>
I must know!<br>
<br>
-Wu <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uiskandaralazeem.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Iskandar Alazeem</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guardian of the Battlefield</BR>STEEL WARRIOR Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 871<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/12/02 7:06:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1398.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Just one question</span><hr size=1> About a month ago, I was in talks with a couple of people from Verant. Never did I say I wanted monks to be nerfed. In fact, I remember specifically saying I *didn't* want monks to be nerfed. I wanted what many other warriors wanted - to be put on a separate defensive table. Small upgrade to taunt would round that out nicely, but I could do without it.<br>
<br>
Yes, I was a little upset when the monks in my guild owned me in every way in exp groups. I didn't think it was balanced, not at all. But never did I call for monks to be nerfed.<br>
<br>
Do not stereotype all of us without knowing firsthand where everyone is coming from. Yes, I think the taunting from warriors at Monkly Business is puerile and asinine; don't assume every warrior thinks that way. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uvaraho1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Varaho1</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 881<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/12/02 7:16:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1398.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Just one question</span><hr size=1> Who are worse, the warriors that laugh at people nerfed, or the monks that want to hurt people in real life over things that happen in a game? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uiskandaralazeem.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Iskandar Alazeem</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guardian of the Battlefield</BR>STEEL WARRIOR Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 875<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/12/02 7:19:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1398.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Just one question</span><hr size=1> Either way, both are Very Bad Things. I'm not about to label one bad act as the lesser of two evils here. People on both sides are acting rashly and immaturely; that's all there is to it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ukrazrussian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KrazRussian</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/12/02 10:27:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1398.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Just one question</span><hr size=1> THe only thing warriors wanted was to be able to mitigate damage better than any other class; something we are supposed to already do. THere are only two ways this can be accomplished:<br>
<br>
1) Upgrade warriors (This is what people wanted. Make no mistake, NO ONE on the boards was calling for a nerf to monks)<br>
2) Nerf everyone else (in the spirit of completely tearing down and redoing game mechanics, this is the option VI opted for)<br>
<br>
Are warriors happy? Not in particular, we wanted better mitigation. However, we are finally content, to a certain extent that we have better mitigation than monks; something we were supposed to have all along. <p><center><p><font size = 3 colo = "blue"><b>Wilhelmm D'Averam<br>Warlord of the Apocalypse</b></font></p></center>

