</DIV>
<BR>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uwubaogoldenarmz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wubao Goldenarmz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 207<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/12/02 4:00:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1398.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   &lt;snicker&gt;</span><hr size=1> &quot;In fact, I remember specifically saying I *didn't* want monks to be nerfed.&quot;<br>
<br>
Which of course, the people at VI will translate as an excuse to just nerf whatever the heck they want to! DUH!<br>
