<br>
Does this mean I am happy about the nerf? I don't even know what the nerf will do, and to be quite honest, I don't believe taking away the steak from a kid to make the starving kid happier is the way to fix world hunger. <br>
<br>
Should they nerf monks? Hard to say, I'd prefer to be fixed.<br>
<br>
I've been in a car crash that left me with most of my bones crushed, broken, or cracked, and to see another guy get both leg broken didn't make me feel any better.<br>
<br>
The nerf might or might not affect us as warrior, it might do nothing as far as I know, bottom line, I will not rejoice at seeing anyone losing thing because I am lacking it. <p>Warlord of the brell server
